body_html:
I also got the same issue, but got it fixed by installing tf_nightly using "pip install tf_nightly"
Please be sure that while installing, there shouldnt be any active python sessions or else the install will fail and the import of even the tensorflow will get u errors.
close all active python sessions and install tf_nightly.

body:
I also got the same issue, but got it fixed by installing tf_nightly using "pip install tf_nightly"
Please be sure that while installing, there shouldnt be any active python sessions or else the install will fail and the import of even the tensorflow will get u errors. 
close all active python sessions and install tf_nightly.
